# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 13. Hora-Trimsamsa Degree Ranges (72)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Each entry maps a degree range within a sign to the specific being
# activated by the intersection of hora (Sun/Moon) and trimsamsa lord.
# Odd signs: Sun hora 0-15°, Moon hora 15-30°
# Even signs: Moon hora 0-15°, Sun hora 15-30°
# Jupiter bridges both horas in every sign.

# ── Dhata (Aries, odd) ──

jyotish:dhata-surya-mangala  a jyotish:DegreeRange ; jyotish:ofAditya jyotish:dhata ;
    jyotish:startDegree 0 ; jyotish:endDegree 5 ;
    jyotish:hora jyotish:surya ; jyotish:trimsamsaLord jyotish:mangala ;
    jyotish:activeBeing jyotish:tumburu .

jyotish:dhata-surya-shani  a jyotish:DegreeRange ; jyotish:ofAditya jyotish:dhata ;
    jyotish:startDegree 5 ; jyotish:endDegree 10 ;
