    jyotish:activeBeing jyotish:heti .

jyotish:dhata-surya-guru  a jyotish:DegreeRange ; jyotish:ofAditya jyotish:dhata ;
    jyotish:startDegree 10 ; jyotish:endDegree 15 ;
    jyotish:hora jyotish:surya ; jyotish:trimsamsaLord jyotish:guru ;
    jyotish:activeBeing jyotish:pulastya .

